headline: ONTO Q4 Earnings Lag Estimates, Fall Y/Y, Revenues Meet on AI Tailwinds
summary: Onto Innovation tops $1B in annual revenue as AI-driven inspection demand and a $240M HBM deal fuel growth, with Q1 2026 outlook signaling margin recovery.
